INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("272", "1", "2019-09-13 04:23:40", "2019-09-13 04:23:40", "[smartslider3 slider=12]		\n			<h1>Meet Silverado Air Systems</h1>		\n		<p>Too many times in this industry, we find that people rarely have a face to put with a name. Here at Silverado Air Systems, we like to provide visual references for the customer so they can preview who they will be coming in contact with on the jobsite and beyond the confines of the workday. Here are some of our family here at Silverado Air Systems, take your time to browse some of the friendly faces representing our fine company!</p><h1>Why Silverado?</h1><p>You may ask yourself, \"Why would I want to work for Silverado Air Systems?\"</p><p>The answer is simple, we are dedicated to the finest quality of service. What this entails is an equal dedication to the improvement of our employees lives.  How many companies say that anymore? Sadly, very few are willing to invest in their employees to the effect that we do. Where this has the biggest impact is in the personal lives and happiness of our employees. By helping our employees improve their situations in life, we have found that their quality of work improves drastically and dramatically. By improving jobsite morale, we have found that our valued customers respond well to a productive, respectful, and happy jobsite crew.  Ultimately, it is about you, and what you search for in an employer.</p>", "Meet Silverado", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "10-revision-v1", "", "", "2019-09-13 04:23:40", "2019-09-13 04:23:40", "", "10", "http://edgwebsitepreview2.info/10-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
